            "title": "GRAND SEASONS「樓王」1105萬沽 每呎售價1.54萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"GRAND SEASONS「樓王」1105萬沽，每呎售價1.54萬。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d7221fac244205547b073a84477a4fb1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250315/_2025031521530065298.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">GRAND SEASONS「樓王」1105萬沽，每呎售價1.54萬。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>會德豐地產與港鐵合作發的將軍澳日出康城GRAND SEASONS，今日錄3房1套「樓王」成交，為1B座19樓A室，面積716方呎，以1,105.2萬元成交，呎價15,436元。\n\n</p>\n<p>而PARK SEASONS第2B座35樓F室，面積323方呎，則以474.7萬元成交，呎價約14,697元。整個SEASONS系列自去年3月開售至今，累售1049伙，套現逾65.1億元。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
